#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:675
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "&percnt;"
msgstr "&percnt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:677
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Used instead of the <guibutton>=</guibutton> key, <guibutton>%</guibutton> "
"interprets the final operation carried out in the current calculation as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"Bya i <guibutton> = </guibutton> Urufunguzo , <guibutton> % </guibutton> i "
"Bihera Igikorwa Inyuma in i KIGEZWEHO Imibare  Nka : "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is + or - the second argument is interpreted as "
"percentage of the first operand."
msgstr ""
"i Bihera Mukoresha ni + Cyangwa - i ISEGONDA ni Nka Ijanisha Bya i "
"Itangira . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:687
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is * divide the result of the multiplication by 100."
msgstr ""
"i Bihera Mukoresha ni * Kugabanya i Igisubizo Bya i Gukuba (*) ku 100 . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the final operator is / give the left operand as a percentage of the "
"right operand."
msgstr "i Bihera Mukoresha ni /i Ibumoso: Nka A Ijanisha Bya i Iburyo: . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:696
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In all other cases the &percnt; key gives identical results to the = key."
msgstr ""
"Byose Ikindi i &percnt; Urufunguzo birasa ibisubizo Kuri i = Urufunguzo . "

